{
  "_comment": [
    "Word count with fully partitioner-managed placement and topology.",
    "",
    "placement:'all' nodes are expanded to one copy per machine automatically.",
    "  load       → load_0, load_1          (each reads the locally staged corpus)",
    "  distribute → distribute_0, distribute_1",
    "  map_n      → map_n_0_{0..3}, map_n_1_{0..3}  (fanout:4 applied per machine)",
    "  aggregate  → aggregate_0, aggregate_1  (each collects its machine's map outputs)",
    "",
    "shared_inputs is auto-derived from the 'load' Input node; no need to declare it.",
    "",
    "Auto-placed nodes: aggregate_global, reduce, save.",
    "  The partitioner assigns these based on 'hints' below.",
    "",
    "Switch 'hints' to try different scenarios:",
    "  balanced: {capacity:{0:0.5, 1:0.5}, host_limit:{0:12,1:12}}",
    "  skewed:   {capacity:{0:0.85,1:0.15},host_limit:{0:12,1:1}}",
    "  no hints: remove the hints field entirely"
  ],
  "shm_path_prefix": "/dev/shm/rdma_wc_ap",
  "log_level": "info",
  "transfer": true,
  "total_nodes": 2,
  "hints": {
    "capacity":   { "0": 0.5,  "1": 0.5  },
    "host_limit": { "0": 12,   "1": 12   }
  },
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "load", "placement": "all", "deps": [],
      "kind": { "Input": { "path": "TestData/corpus_large.txt", "prefetch": true } }
    },
    {
      "id": "distribute", "placement": "all", "deps": ["load"],
      "kind": { "Func": { "func": "wc_distribute", "out_base": 10 } }
    },
    {
      "id": "map_n", "placement": "all", "fanout": 8, "deps": ["distribute"],
      "kind": { "Func": { "func": "wc_map", "output_offset": 100 } }
    },
    {
      "id": "aggregate", "placement": "all", "deps": ["map_n"],
      "kind": { "Aggregate": {} }
    },
    {
      "id": "aggregate_global", "deps": ["aggregate"],
      "kind": { "Aggregate": {} }
    },
    {
      "id": "reduce", "deps": ["aggregate_global"],
      "kind": { "Func": { "func": "wc_reduce" } }
    },
    {
      "id": "save", "deps": ["reduce"],
      "kind": { "Output": { "path": "TestOutput/wc_auto_placement_result.txt" } }
    }
  ]
}
